title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a highlight or map, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: Exporting the data from the table should successfully export the data, without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce: 
1. Open the attached report.
2. Export the data from the table.

Expected Result: The data should be exported successfully.
Actual Result: An exception occurs in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
